flowchart TD
    PodRequest[Pod Requests: CPU 2, Mem 4Gi] --> Evaluation{Resource Placement Strategy}
    
    subgraph Bin Packing Strategy
        direction TB
        MostAllocated[NodeResourcesFit Plugin<br/>MostAllocated Strategy]
        PackedNode[Fill nodes to maximum before opening new ones]
        Saver[Saves cloud costs by grouping workloads]
    end

    subgraph Spreading Strategy
        direction TB
        LeastAllocated[NodeResourcesFit Plugin<br/>LeastAllocated Strategy]
        SpreadNode[Distribute resources evenly across all nodes]
        Perf[Prevents CPU starvation & hotspots]
    end

    Evaluation -->|Cost / Autoscaling Optimized| BinPacking[Bin Packing Setup]
    Evaluation -->|Performance / High Availability| Spreading[Spreading Setup]

    BinPacking --> MostAllocated --> PackedNode --> Saver
    Spreading --> LeastAllocated --> SpreadNode --> Perf
